## Key Design Decisions

1. **Single timer for all phases** вЂ” avoids timer lifecycle bugs and keeps state machine as single source of truth
2. **Math-based animation** вЂ” SwiftUI animations drift over many breaths; computing from elapsed time keeps counter and circle in sync
3. **Explicit timestamps on CycleRecord** вЂ” makes chart phase overlays trivial to compute
4. **HKWorkoutSession** вЂ” guarantees continuous HR sampling vs sporadic passive observation
5. **SwiftData cascade delete** вЂ” deleting a session cleans up all child records automatically
